node.text:
2 story custom wine tower recently completed by @advancedwoodwork for a luxury residence in Indian Wells, California.

It holds over 2000 wine bottles and is motorized and rotates. The wine pegs were installed in a such a way that when the tower moves,  it mimics a DNA strand. 🧬

The  30 ft tall steel structure is clad in Ash veneer and is the perfect centerpiece to this amazing home  🍷 🍷 🍷 

@advancedwoodwork
